{"tid":858923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] 今年洛杉磯快艇pick咗pokemon入面個小剛入隊！","createTime":"2018-10-12T06:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:45:21.000Z","uid":154872,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66e762b3f48a845274840b27456f26a171acfd43","tid":858923,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"有推特網友發現，洛杉磯快艇菜鳥Jerome Robinson竟然和日本人氣動畫《精靈寶可夢》中的主要配角「小剛」撞臉，Robinson在推特上看到後忍不住笑翻，一拿起照片來對比，更讓在場隊友們笑到失控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgiZByp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgiZByp.jpg&h=210de939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲快艇菜鳥Jerome Robinson撞臉動畫角色，笑翻網友。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n21歲的Robinson主打得分後衛，是快艇在今夏選秀會上首輪13順位選進，就讀波士頓學院時曾在一場NCAA賽事砍下46分，投入選秀前，在大三球季35場先發出賽中，以4成85命中率取得場均20.7分成績。<br />\n<br />\nRobinson微笑時的瞇瞇眼，和《精靈寶可夢》中的「小剛」如出一轍，由於小剛在動畫中的個性設定是以「看到美女就會衝動上前搭訕」為人所知，網友們擔心Robinson會和小剛一樣失控，不禁笑說「慘了，以後快艇要取消啦啦隊了」。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AC%91%E7%BF%BB-%E5%BF%AB%E8%89%87%E8%8F%9C%E9%B3%A5%E7%AB%9F%E6%92%9E%E8%87%89%E5%AF%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A2-%E5%B0%8F%E5%89%9B-042222748.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25AC%2591%25E7%25BF%25BB-%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%2589%2587%25E8%258F%259C%25E9%25B3%25A5%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%2587%2589%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A2-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2589%259B-042222748.html&d=6JrVqrMZ%2BG20ESSJulJ3SKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b14f793a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AC%91%E7%BF%BB-%E5%BF%AB%E8%89%87%E8%8F%9C%E9%B3%A5%E7%AB%9F%E6%92%9E%E8%87%89%E5%AF%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A2-%E5%B0%8F%E5%89%9B-042222748.html</a>"},{"pid":"0636e67fd6e066b23d9bbcbc67b708f59c32e822","tid":858923,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ae7dfcba53a17511b174f87598e7f21adb75ba","